OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBlustery
OL,6,Fshowers will retreat to western coasts
OL,7,Ffrom the late evening. With increasing
OL,8,Fclear spells and the wind falling
OL,9,Flight, a patchy frost is expected in
OL,10,Fthe east. Coastal gales in the evening
OL,11,Fwill ease overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FMostly dry with bright spells
OL,14,Fand a few showers in the west in the
OL,15,Fmorning. Cloud and scattered showers
OL,16,Fspread northeast during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
