OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith sunny periods Tuesday. Cloud and
OL,7,Frain spread northeast late Tuesday,
OL,8,Fclearing through Wednesday. Showers
OL,9,Ffollow later Wednesday into Thursday,
OL,10,Fheavy at times. Occasionally windy
OL,11,FWednesday and Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
